subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Those who know CiCi Bellis, the 15-year-old who defeated 12th-seeded Dominika Cibulkova in the first round of the U.S. Open on Tuesday, say her burst onto the scene is not surprising given her maturity.
